<H3>Refunds</H3>
<P>When you've purchased marking services from Exambuff, you may request a refund at any time up until it has been accepting for marking by one of our markers. Beyond this point, no refund is possible.</P> <P>To request a refund login to your account and use the 'refund' button of the answer you desire to cancel and refund.</P> 